            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EMoney%20does%20not%20satisfy.%20Had%20it%20satisfied%20the%20queen%20of%20Sheba%2C%20she%20never%20would%20have%20traveled%20for%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20over%20ancient%20roads%20and%20deserts%20just%20to%20hear%20the%20words%20of%20God%20from%20Solomon.%20The%20human%20heart%20craves%20more%20than%20money.%20It%20craves%20answers%20to%20life's%20purpose%20and%20longs%20to%20see%20the%20wisdom%20and%20power%20of%20God.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESimon%20was%20willing%20to%20pay%20money%20to%20obtain%20the%20power%20of%20laying%20hands%20on%20people%20to%20receive%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20(Acts%208%3A18-19).%20The%20treasurer%20for%20Candace%2C%20the%20queen%20of%20Ethiopia%2C%20was%20more%20interested%20in%20knowing%20whom%20Isaiah%20was%20describing%20than%20he%20was%20in%20acquiring%20all%20the%20wealth%20of%20which%20he%20was%20steward%20(v.%2034).%20Even%20Solomon%20with%20his%20hundreds%20of%20talents%20of%20gold%20per%20year%20was%20not%20satisfied%20with%20worldly%20wealth%2C%20and%20his%20wandering%2C%20searching%20heart%20thus%20delved%20into%20idolatry.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EDon't%20let%20the%20devil%20dangle%20riches%20before%20your%20eyes%2C%20telling%20you%20that%20money%20will%20fulfill%20you.%20Those%20who%20have%20handled%20vast%20sums%20of%20it%20will%20tell%20you%20otherwise.%20Use%20money%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20evangelize%20the%20world%2C%20and%20enjoy%20the%20free%20riches%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
